title: Arminna West
description: Archaeological site located on the Nile with late Nubian, Meroitic, and early Christian remains. The site was inundated as a result of the construction of the Aswan High Dam in the 1960s.

properties.description: Point representing the approximate location of the inundated Arminna West site, after Weeks 1967.
